---
title: Sweet and Sticky Chicken with Brown Rice
description: This sticky chicken is finger lickin’ good fun, and an absolute weeknight winner. It takes no time at all to whip up, and the combination of fish sauce and brown sugar transforms your tender chicken into sticky morsels bursting with flavour. Licking the plate clean is heartily encouraged!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-and-sticky-chicken-5b6e4bf5.jpg
